<exercise checkit-seed="0009" checkit-slug="CC2" checkit-title="Constant-Coefficient Linear Non-Homogeneous First-Order IVPs">
  <statement>
    <p>Explain how to find the particular solution to the given IVP.</p>
    <me>-4 \, {y'} = -24 \, \cos\left(2 \, t\right) e^{\left(5 \, t\right)} - 20 \, {y};\qquad y(0)=3</me>
  </statement>
  <answer>
    <me>y=3 \, e^{\left(5 \, t\right)} \sin\left(2 \, t\right) + 3 \, e^{\left(5 \, t\right)}</me>
  </answer>
</exercise>
